<h2>Deployment</h2>

<p>To run the theme locally, navigate to the theme directory and run <code>bundle install</code> to install the dependencies, then run <code>jekyll serve</code> or <code>bundle exec serve</code> to start the Jekyll server.</p>

<p>I would recommend checking the <a href="https://jekyllrb.com/docs/deployment-methods/">Deployment Methods</a> page on Jekyll website.</p>

